> I need to output contents with utf8 encoding in CGI scripts.
> Can you tell me how to open STDOUT with utf8 support?Thanks you.
> 
Hello,

Just do,
binmode(STDOUT, ":utf8");

see "perldoc perluniintro" for more details.

